data.description: Beautiful ranch home located in the Wedgewood section of Oceanside. Many updates include a gorgeous kitchen featuring gas cooking, pot filler, tiled backsplash, granite counters, pantry , open concept with pendant lighting, and top of the line stainless appliances. Each room is filled with natural light from the multiple windows and glass sliding doors. The primary bedroom features a king size bed complete with ensuite bath, two additional bedrooms and a newly remodeled main bath that is stunning. The backyard has a cement patio, basketball area, room for a vegetable garden and golf course views.  A one car attached garage, cement driveway, and low taxes complete the property.
